	title="Canada vs India Outsourcing Quality Comparison - Complete Analysis | InfraDev Consulting" 
	description="Compare outsourcing software development to Canada vs. India. Compare quality, communication, time zones, cultural alignment, cost, and project success factors for U.S. companies."
	canonical={pageUrl}
